== 小艾伯特实验 ==
{{main|小艾伯特实验}}
华生和雷顿进行的[[小艾伯特实验|小艾伯特实验]]，是心理学中最具争议性的实验之一。这个不朽的实验被记载在心理学教科书中。<!-- 这个实验的目标是 show how principles of, 当时recently discovered, [[古典制约|古典制约]] could 应用于 condition fear of a 白鼠into "[[小艾伯特实验|小艾伯特实验]]", an 11月大的男孩，由于小艾伯特的故事has made the rounds, inaccuracies and inconsistencies have crept in, some of them even due to 华生自己; see Harris for an analysis. The controversy about this experiment 事实上 a 现代发展。There seemed to be little concern about it in Watson's time。Dewsbury reports 华生受到 received greater criticism from early animal rights groups over some of his experiments with rats, particularly a 1907 study, "Kinaesthetic and Organic Sensations: Their Role in the Reactions of 白鼠 to the Maze." -->

== 晚年 ==

1936年，华生停止写普及读物，在65岁时从广告业退休。罗莎莉·雷纳已经在1935年，36岁时去世。他在晚年和一位女伴居住在一个农场。在医生的劝告下，华生戒除了酒瘾，在晚年身体健康。他在1958年去世，享年80岁，去世前不久，美国心理学会表彰了他对心理学的贡献。<!-- 历史学家 John Burnham 访谈晚年的华生，and reported him to be a man of (still) strong opinions and some bitterness towards his detractors.  Except for a set of reprints of his academic works, Watson burned his very large collection of letters and personal papers, thus depriving historians of a valuable resource for understanding the early history of behaviorism and Watson himself. -->

